DBD-Simulated version 0.01
==========================

Ever tried to test any DBI-based module's error handling?

DBD::Simulated is able to report any error you ask for.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  DBI is suggested but not really required.

